    "contextResponses": [
        {
            "contextElement": {
                "attributes": [
                    {
                        "name": "A1", 
                        "type": "", 
                        "value": ""
                    }
                ], 
                "id": "E1", 
                "isPattern": "false", 
                "type": "T1"
            }, 
            "statusCode": {
                "code": "200", 
                "reasonPhrase": "OK"
            }
        }
    ]
}


03. Update/UPDATE E1/T1/A1=1 and see it work (PUT /v1/contextEntities/E1/attributes/A1?entity::type=T1)
=======================================================================================================
HTTP/1.1 200 OK
Content-Length: 34
Content-Type: application/json
Fiware-Correlator: REGEX([0-9a-f\-]{36})
